OL,3,CMexican man wins claim against Cartier
OL,4,Cafter buying earrings for only #22
OL,6,FRogelio Villarreal waited four months
OL,7,Fto finally receive the deal of the
OL,8,Fcentury, David Harper reports
OL,10,FA man won a claim against Cartier
OL,11,Fafter he managed to buy two pairs of
OL,12,Fearrings for only #22 after the luxury
OL,13,Fjeweler accidentally listed them on
OL,14,Ftheir website at the wrong price.
OL,16,FRogelio Villarreal was browsing
OL,17,FInstagram when he spotted a pair of
OL,18,Frose gold, diamond-encrusted earrings
OL,19,Fbeing sold for MX$237 (#11).
