OL,3,CMexican man wins claim against Cartier
OL,4,Cafter buying earrings for only #22
OL,6,F"I swear I broke out in a cold sweat,"
OL,7,Fhe wrote on X, formerly Twitter.
OL,9,FMr Villarreal bought two pairs before
OL,10,Fthe price was quickly corrected to
OL,11,FMX$237,000 (#11,046).
OL,13,FCartier declined to recognise the
OL,14,Fpurchase and offered him a full
OL,15,Frefund, a bottle of champagne, and a
OL,16,Fpassport holder - but Mr Villarreal
OL,17,Fdeclined the offer and waited four
OL,18,Fmonths for his earrings to arrive.
