OL,6,FDuring the dispute, he asked Mexico's
OL,7,Fconsumer protection agency to get
OL,8,Finvolved, who ruled in his favour.
OL,9,FOverall, he managed to save around
OL,10,F#29,500.
OL,12,FSimilar earrings on the British
OL,13,FCartier website sell for #14,800.
OL,15,FMr Villarreal shared the story on
OL,16,FTikTok and attracted a large audience
OL,17,Fas he waited for his deal of the
OL,18,Fcentury to arrive.
OL,20,FAfter they arrived, he shared a
OL,21,Fpicture of him posing in the earrings.
